{
  "stem": "10181.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "At that age, you learn very quickly by playing outside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I started going to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's a regular-- in that area, they had always two schools.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most of Holland has two [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There's a very big Catholic population.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They have a Catholic school and then a general school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So everybody who wasn't Catholic went to the general school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So all the Jewish kids of course, went to the general school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in that town-- in that little town, there were not-- were not that many Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In Holland, they-- the Jews in almost every-- every town, every little place were Dutch Jews, not-- not German Jews.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in this particular little town, there were just a few families.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But when the German Jews came, that's when the Jewish population relatively grew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It still wasn't very big.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was no-- there was no proper synagogue.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was like a little room, you know, where they prayed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- and I would say the majority were German Jews, yeah, not-- not Dutch Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But life was, except for my mother not being there, was very normal, you know, because Holland wasn't at war or anything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And neither was Germany [INAUDIBLE] still.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But, you know, there was no anti-Semitic laws.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I mean, the Jews were treated like everybody else.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The only thing is we were-- we were foreigners, basically.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We weren't Dutch.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But even that didn't really bother us, except there was sort of an incident which I remember well because it sort of was, you know, a big thing.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I had two uncles who came to live at the same house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "These were the husbands of two sisters of my father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "My father had a lot of brothers and sisters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There were seven all together.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
